Summary: Biochemical reaction from 4-hydroxypropofol to 4-hydroxypropofol sulfate. This interaction is catalyzed by SULT1A1.
Biochemical reaction from 4-hydroxypropofol to 4-hydroxypropofol 4-glucuronide. This interaction is catalyzed by UGT1A9.
Biochemical reaction from propofol to propofol glucuronide. This interaction is catalyzed by UGT1A9.
Biochemical reaction from 4-hydroxypropofol to 4-hydroxypropofol 1-glucuronide. This interaction is catalyzed by UGT1A9.
Biochemical reaction from propofol to 4-hydroxypropofol. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C9 or CYP2B6.
